snippet.title: Pigeon Simulator - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Pigeon Simulator Takes Flight! 🐦

No bird of a lie, we’re thrilled to announce that Bossa Studios has officially begun work on the ultimate crapshoot - Pigeon Simulator!

Further news will be hatching soon, but in the meantime, check out the im-peck-able announcement trailer above!

Stay abreast of the latest Pigeon Simulator happenings here 👉 http://www.pigeonsimulator.com
